Hi Jacob,

I was informed that the setup steps for Entra are the same as for Azure AD, which you can find in the EPP manual, in chapters 13.2.Azure Active Directory and 16.12. Single Sign On and :
https://www.endpointprotector.com/support/pdf/manual/Endpoint_Protector_5_User_Manual_EN.pdf

Regarding the verification of groups, you have to do it manually, by comparing the groups from Entra, to the groups on the EPP server. You can also export the groups:
